<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN253">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>eṉṟiṟat tavalaṅ koḷḷa liṉiyē</l>
<l>vavvār kaṇṇi yiḷaiyar tiḷaippa</l>
<l>nakāaleṉa vanta māṟē yeḻāneṟ</l>
<l>paiṅkaḻai potikaḷain taṉṉa viḷarppiṉ</l>
<l>vaḷaiyil vaṟuṅkai yōccik</l>
<l>kiḷaiyu ḷoyvalō kūṟuniṉ ṉuraiyē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>  Don’t feel suffering on my behalf. Now,</l>
<l>  while young men with chaplets swing, not snatching,</l>
<l>  because [I] came, saying “I won’t smile”, </l>
<l>  will I wield, in [my] empty hand without bangles, </l>
<l>  the whiteness that is as if removing ungrown paddy from fresh bamboo,</l>
<l>  [and] carry [it] among [my] kin? [Just] say your words.</l>
</lg>
